OL,4,CStreaming TV giants face tighter UK
OL,5,Cregulation
OL,6, Services like Netflix, Amazon Prime and
OL,7, Disney+ could face tighter regulation
OL,8, in the UK under government proposals.
OL,10,FTraditional broadcasters like the BBC
OL,11,Fand ITV have to comply with regulator
OL,12,FOfcom's code covering issues like harm,
OL,13,Foffence, accuracy and impartiality. But
OL,14,Fmost streaming platforms do not.
OL,16,FThe government has announced a review
OL,17,Finto whether to strengthen the rules.
OL,19,FMeanwhile, ministers have also
OL,20,Fconfirmed a consultation into whether
OL,21,Fto privatise Channel 4.
